## 2026-02-22 â€” Initial conventions

### Data model
- `ListItem` has fields `status: WatchStatus?`, `currentSeason: Int?`, `currentEpisode: Int?`
- `WatchStatus` enum: `WATCHED`, `IN_PROGRESS`, `PLAN_TO_WATCH`
- Default when adding to a list â€” `PLAN_TO_WATCH` (not `null`)
- Legacy records with `status = null` are treated as `PLAN_TO_WATCH` in the UI

### Progress management
- Changing status and episode â€” **only on the media detail page** (`/media/[mediaId]`)
- On list cards â€” status display only (icon), no editing

### Media cards
- Grid: `grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-3 xl:grid-cols-5`
- Card is a `<a>` link with `group relative overflow-hidden`
- Hover overlay â€” `absolute inset-x-0 bottom-0`, `opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100`
- Status icon â€” `absolute top-2 right-2` with `style="background-color: ..."` (not a dynamic Tailwind class)
- Bottom panel: `p-3 transition-opacity group-hover:opacity-0`

### Home page filters
- URL params: `q`, `genre`, `status`, `yearFrom`, `yearTo`
- "All" in a Select filter: sentinel `'__all__'` instead of an empty string

### Select component
- Always `Select.Root type="single"` or `type="multiple"` â€” omitting `type` causes a TypeScript error
- Native `<select>` is forbidden

### Country flags
- Computed via Unicode offset `127397` (= `U+1F1E6` âˆ’ 65)
- `formatCountry(code)` in `$shared/lib/labels.ts`

### Icons
- `circle-check` (not `check-circle`), `circle-play` (not `play-circle`) â€” deprecated variants have no `.svelte.d.ts`

### Global CSS transitions (`app.css`)
- `button`: `transition-all duration-150`, `active:scale-[0.97]`
- `a`: `transition-colors duration-150`
- `input:focus-visible`: ring via `color-mix(in srgb, var(--ring) 50%, transparent)`

